<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Register WEB</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 2px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        ul {
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }
        ul li {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button:hover {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #0056b3;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Selamat Datang</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hallo <%= username %>,</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorem, obcaecati deleniti. Suscipit, consequatur fugiat ipsum obcaecati quasi est aliquid accusamus?</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Nama:</strong> <%= fullName %></li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></li>
                <li><strong>Tanggal Pendaftaran:</strong> <%= createdAt %></li>
            </ul>
            <p>Untuk memulai, silakan klik tombol di bawah ini:</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="button">Aktifkan Akun</a></p>
            <p>Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami.</p>
            <p>Salam hangat,<br>Acara</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Acara Event Management System. Semua hak dilindungi.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
